Feature: Simulating the Draft

  Background:
    Given I am a User

  Scenario: In order to get a real time update
    Then I want to see the results of the draft by round and by NFL Team

  Scenario: In order to see which players are still draftable
    Then I want to be able to view all remaining players alphabetically by position

  Scenario: In order to see only what is actively happening
    Then I want to see the latest 3 picks and which team is next to pick

